      • setGenreDescription

        public void setGenreDescription(String text)
                         throws IllegalArgumentException
        Description copied from interface: ID3v2
        Set genre from text. This method behaves different depending on the ID3 version. Prior to ID3v2.4, the provided text must match a id3v1 genre description. With ID3v2.4, the genre is written as free text.
        Specified by:
